body.description: Repair and soften thick hair with OGX Extra Strength Damage Remedy + Coconut Miracle Oil Penetrating Hair Oil Treatment. Ideal for medium to coarse-textures, medium to dry hydration levels, and medium to high volume hair types, the hydrating oil treatment penetrates each strand to help tame frizzy hair and flyaways, transforming hair into silky smooth perfection. The nourishing blend contains coconut oil to help add luster, shine & softness to hair along with vanilla bean extract and essence of tiare - an infused perfume-oil made from soaking the petals in coconut oil. Plus, the coconut milk, tangerine and warm vanilla scent makes hair care an all-around sensory experience and leaves locks with an irresistibly good smell. Paraben-free and sulfated-surfactants free, this restorative coconut hair represents beauty, pure and simple.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: We approach beauty in our own way, pure and simple Originality inspires us, that’s why we love being different; from our exotic ingredients, to the shape of our bottles, to our quest for sustainability. Nourshing + Coconut Milk Shampoo This exclusive blend with coconut milk, egg white proteins and coconut oils helps bring out your hair’s natural strength, elasticity, hydration and balance-all with a shine inspired by the tropics. Is your hair ready for a tropical vacation? Retreat to the islands. Deeply nourishing shampoo Helps hydrate & strengthen Leaves hair soft and hydrated Coconut Milk & Coconut Oils Sulfate free surfactants hair care system

Benefits This creamy blend, infused with Coconut Milk, whipped Egg White Proteins and Coconut Oils helps nourish from root to tip to bring out your hair's natural strength and elasticity. Expect super shine and a subtle scent of coconut with every swish.Get ready to be transported to the tropics! Ingredients Infused with coconut milk, whipped egg proteins and coconut oils. This deliciously creamy and nourishing blend, helps to strengthen and hydrate your hair, leaving it softly scented, super soft and glowing. Hair Types This product is good for everyday use. Works well with all hair types: - Fine. - Oily. - Frizzy. - Straight. Regimen For best results, use our entire Nourshing + Coconut Milk Shampoo collection to help with every day moisture. After shampooing, we recommend our Nourshing + Coconut Milk Conditioner followed up with one of the treatments to help moisturize and restore shine to all hair types.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Get Luscious Locks with OGX Nourishing + Coconut Milk Moisturizing Shampoo
reviews.reviewText: Are you tired of having dry and lifeless hair? Look no further than the OGX Nourishing + Coconut Milk Moisturizing Shampoo! I recently tried this shampoo and I am absolutely in love with it.The coconut milk in this shampoo provides intense moisture to your hair, leaving it feeling soft and silky smooth. The formula is also sulfate-free, which means it's gentle enough for all hair types, including color-treated hair.Not only does this shampoo work wonders on your hair, but it also smells amazing! The tropical coconut scent is refreshing and invigorating, making it the perfect addition to your morning routine.Overall, I highly recommend the OGX Nourishing + Coconut Milk Moisturizing Shampoo to anyone looking for a high-quality, moisturizing shampoo that smells great and works wonders on your hair. Give it a try and see the difference for yourself!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for thickening up hair!
reviews.reviewText: I am absolutely thrilled with the OGX Nourishing Coconut Milk Shampoo! From the very first use, I noticed a remarkable difference in the health and appearance of my hair. I've used it for about three years now and, after having thin, flat hair up until then, I've had insane amounts of volume since because of this shampoo.The coconut milk formula has worked wonders in replenishing moisture to my dry, flat hair, leaving it feeling soft, smooth, and voluminous. The coconut scent is a great added bonus! I couldn't be happier with the results - its a game-changer, and I highly recommend it to anyone trying to revive their hair!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 1, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This product smells so good. Its kind of hard to describe, but it almost smells like a really sweet coconut cookie. In terms of effectiveness, I have been using the product for quite a while, and it has shown significant improvement in my hair. My hair can get very dry and is also very thin, but using this shampoo consistently has made my hair more hydrated but not stripped, clean, and it seems to have even helped with the strength of my hair. The smell is also pretty long-lasting too. Overall, it is a quite good shampoo, but if it doesn't work, there are definitely other options out there.
